By now, your town hall should have finished upgrading. Use a peon from the gold mines to build a bestiary and spirit lodge. Summon a second hero at the altar of storms. At the bestiary, research, ensnare, war drums, and  envenomed spears. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/9/95/Win-a-1-vs.-1-Battle-in-Warcraft-3-as-an-Orc-Step-6Bullet1.jpg/v4-460px-Win-a-1-vs.-1-Battle-in-Warcraft-3-as-an-Orc-Step-6Bullet1.jpg","bigUrl":"/images/thumb/9/95/Win-a-1-vs.-1-Battle-in-Warcraft-3-as-an-Orc-Step-6Bullet1.jpg/aid187037-v4-728px-Win-a-1-vs.-1-Battle-in-Warcraft-3-as-an-Orc-Step-6Bullet1.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":"728","bigHeight":"546","licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

At the spirit lodge, research witch doctor adept training and shaman adept training. Also, train a few shaman and a couple witch doctors and a couple kodo beasts and raiders. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/1/1b/Win-a-1-vs.-1-Battle-in-Warcraft-3-as-an-Orc-Step-6Bullet2.jpg/v4-460px-Win-a-1-vs.-1-Battle-in-Warcraft-3-as-an-Orc-Step-6Bullet2.jpg","bigUrl":"/images/thumb/1/1b/Win-a-1-vs.-1-Battle-in-Warcraft-3-as-an-Orc-Step-6Bullet2.jpg/aid187037-v4-728px-Win-a-1-vs.-1-Battle-in-Warcraft-3-as-an-Orc-Step-6Bullet2.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":"728","bigHeight":"546","licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

While doing this, upgrade your stronghold. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/4/45/Win-a-1-vs.-1-Battle-in-Warcraft-3-as-an-Orc-Step-6Bullet3.jpg/v4-460px-Win-a-1-vs.-1-Battle-in-Warcraft-3-as-an-Orc-Step-6Bullet3.jpg","bigUrl":"/images/thumb/4/45/Win-a-1-vs.-1-Battle-in-Warcraft-3-as-an-Orc-Step-6Bullet3.jpg/aid187037-v4-728px-Win-a-1-vs.-1-Battle-in-Warcraft-3-as-an-Orc-Step-6Bullet3.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":"728","bigHeight":"546","licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

Now, with 2 heroes and 3 grunts, a couple raiders, a couple kodo beasts, a couple witch doctors, and a few shaman you can try creeping red dots. Expand (clear out a gold mine close to your camp, build a great hall there,and train peons to gather gold and lumber). {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/2/25/Win-a-1-vs.-1-Battle-in-Warcraft-3-as-an-Orc-Step-7Bullet1.jpg/v4-460px-Win-a-1-vs.-1-Battle-in-Warcraft-3-as-an-Orc-Step-7Bullet1.jpg","bigUrl":"/images/thumb/2/25/Win-a-1-vs.-1-Battle-in-Warcraft-3-as-an-Orc-Step-7Bullet1.jpg/aid187037-v4-728px-Win-a-1-vs.-1-Battle-in-Warcraft-3-as-an-Orc-Step-7Bullet1.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":"728","bigHeight":"546","licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

Hunt for enemy expansions if you don't feel like creeping or if all the creeps near your side are gone. While doing this, you should build a few more burrows. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/9/94/Win-a-1-vs.-1-Battle-in-Warcraft-3-as-an-Orc-Step-7Bullet2.jpg/v4-460px-Win-a-1-vs.-1-Battle-in-Warcraft-3-as-an-Orc-Step-7Bullet2.jpg","bigUrl":"/images/thumb/9/94/Win-a-1-vs.-1-Battle-in-Warcraft-3-as-an-Orc-Step-7Bullet2.jpg/aid187037-v4-728px-Win-a-1-vs.-1-Battle-in-Warcraft-3-as-an-Orc-Step-7Bullet2.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":"728","bigHeight":"546","licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

When the stronghold finishes, it's your choice if you want the third hero. In the beastiary, train 3-4 wyverns. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/e/e1/Win-a-1-vs.-1-Battle-in-Warcraft-3-as-an-Orc-Step-8Bullet1.jpg/v4-460px-Win-a-1-vs.-1-Battle-in-Warcraft-3-as-an-Orc-Step-8Bullet1.jpg","bigUrl":"/images/thumb/e/e1/Win-a-1-vs.-1-Battle-in-Warcraft-3-as-an-Orc-Step-8Bullet1.jpg/aid187037-v4-728px-Win-a-1-vs.-1-Battle-in-Warcraft-3-as-an-Orc-Step-8Bullet1.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":"728","bigHeight":"546","licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

In the spirit lodge, research shaman master training and witch doctor training, and if any of your units died (other than grunts), replace them. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/0/08/Win-a-1-vs.-1-Battle-in-Warcraft-3-as-an-Orc-Step-8Bullet2.jpg/v4-460px-Win-a-1-vs.-1-Battle-in-Warcraft-3-as-an-Orc-Step-8Bullet2.jpg","bigUrl":"/images/thumb/0/08/Win-a-1-vs.-1-Battle-in-Warcraft-3-as-an-Orc-Step-8Bullet2.jpg/aid187037-v4-728px-Win-a-1-vs.-1-Battle-in-Warcraft-3-as-an-Orc-Step-8Bullet2.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":"728","bigHeight":"546","licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

Use a peon to build a tauren totem and research pulverize. After it finishes researching, train 3-4 tauren. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/8/81/Win-a-1-vs.-1-Battle-in-Warcraft-3-as-an-Orc-Step-8Bullet3.jpg/v4-460px-Win-a-1-vs.-1-Battle-in-Warcraft-3-as-an-Orc-Step-8Bullet3.jpg","bigUrl":"/images/thumb/8/81/Win-a-1-vs.-1-Battle-in-Warcraft-3-as-an-Orc-Step-8Bullet3.jpg/aid187037-v4-728px-Win-a-1-vs.-1-Battle-in-Warcraft-3-as-an-Orc-Step-8Bullet3.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":"728","bigHeight":"546","licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

With all those units and 2-3 heroes and knowing where the enemy is, you should attack. If the enemy masses towers, bring along a few catapults. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/b/bb/Win-a-1-vs.-1-Battle-in-Warcraft-3-as-an-Orc-Step-9Bullet1.jpg/v4-460px-Win-a-1-vs.-1-Battle-in-Warcraft-3-as-an-Orc-Step-9Bullet1.jpg","bigUrl":"/images/thumb/b/bb/Win-a-1-vs.-1-Battle-in-Warcraft-3-as-an-Orc-Step-9Bullet1.jpg/aid187037-v4-728px-Win-a-1-vs.-1-Battle-in-Warcraft-3-as-an-Orc-Step-9Bullet1.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":"728","bigHeight":"546","licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

If you destroy all his towers but the screen doesn't say victory that means he either got a hidden building, a different base hidden somewhere,or a hidden expansion. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/5/53/Win-a-1-vs.-1-Battle-in-Warcraft-3-as-an-Orc-Step-9Bullet2.jpg/v4-460px-Win-a-1-vs.-1-Battle-in-Warcraft-3-as-an-Orc-Step-9Bullet2.jpg","bigUrl":"/images/thumb/5/53/Win-a-1-vs.-1-Battle-in-Warcraft-3-as-an-Orc-Step-9Bullet2.jpg/aid187037-v4-728px-Win-a-1-vs.-1-Battle-in-Warcraft-3-as-an-Orc-Step-9Bullet2.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":"728","bigHeight":"546","licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

Use a goblin laboratory to reveal, or a far seers far sight ability to check out the gold mines. Hunt him down and wait for victory to appear on the screen. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/c/c6/Win-a-1-vs.-1-Battle-in-Warcraft-3-as-an-Orc-Step-9Bullet3.jpg/v4-460px-Win-a-1-vs.-1-Battle-in-Warcraft-3-as-an-Orc-Step-9Bullet3.jpg","bigUrl":"/images/thumb/c/c6/Win-a-1-vs.-1-Battle-in-Warcraft-3-as-an-Orc-Step-9Bullet3.jpg/aid187037-v4-728px-Win-a-1-vs.-1-Battle-in-Warcraft-3-as-an-Orc-Step-9Bullet3.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":"728","bigHeight":"546","licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}
